row.Body: <!DOCTYPE html> <html> <head> <meta charset="utf-8" /> <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" /> <title>{{Survey.Title}}</title> <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bulma@0.9.2/css/bulma.min.css" /> <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://gitcdn.link/cdn/Wikiki/bulma-checkradio/38c95578f465f4c3805f578490925f337b87404d/dist/css/bulma-checkradio.min.css" /> <style></style> </head> <body class="has-background-light" style="height: 100%; min-height: 100vh"> <section class="section container is-max-desktop py-5"> <form class="is-max-desktop has-background-white px-0 py-5 container is-fluid" name="{{Survey.FormName}}" action="{{SurveyURL}}" method="post" enctype="application/x-www-form-urlencoded"> {{InnerContent}} </form> </section> </body> </html>
